{"tid":1285811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」我發咗個惡夢, 有一大班暴徒係屯門公園掟臭蛋。","createTime":"2019-07-04T16:46:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T17:18:03.000Z","uid":256741,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9b3b7fe44b3c972a3aaa3f5b1bd1a49bcd53eb33","tid":1285811,"uid":256741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:46:58.000Z","msg":"個夢好真好科幻！我夢見班暴徒突然出現係各大演唱會場地嘅地下掟臭蛋。臭蛋爆開嘅同時啲暴徒就立即化為雲煙消失於無影無蹤。因為太臭嘅關係搞到大量演唱會要取消，造成屯門公園嚴重經濟損失。<br />\n<br />\n從此以後冇人再敢入個公園開演唱會，因為實在太臭唔適宜長時間停留。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mxRR15a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmxRR15a.jpg&h=812a888b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OHmVKiw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOHmVKiw.jpg&h=b3e49cb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SaiMQYz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSaiMQYz.jpg&h=c021cc37&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"44ffd8a28f51d0f5de508b84d492fee3269a4477","tid":1285811,"uid":82640,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/O3HNAp9.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO3HNAp9.gif&h=9cee48d5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1268c249f91df360c1b8de1f1429c550385295d3","tid":1285811,"uid":239812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:57:49.000Z","msg":"應該引入良幣驅逐劣幣.....<br />\n<br />\n廣傳比佢地上面d同胞 等佢地互喰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d7ad188b0806a05ed9ba43f36379ec7a6df46e","tid":1285811,"uid":131836,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:07:11.000Z","msg":"我見外國成日有d後生係公園練舞<br />\n或者大學danso有無得搞個快閃event打對台<br />\n<br />\n有就狗衝去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01046b502a5679fa53bf633de48077